yn, avait 28 ans. Il a épousé Helen Arbuthnot environ 1343, à Écosse. Ils ont eu au moins 3 fils. Il est décédé en 1365, à Écosse, à l’âge de 73 ans."},"de":{"1292–1365":"1292–1365","1280–Male":"1280–Verstorben","1296–Female":"1296–Verstorben","1328–Female":"1328–Verstorben","1365–Male":"1365–Verstorben","1318–1407":"1318–1407","1320–Male":"1320–Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1261–1306":"1261–1306","1265–Female":"1265–Verstorben","about 1291":"um 1291","1296":"1296","1261":"1261","1292":"1292","abt 1365":"um 1365","1280":"1280","about 1318":"um 1318","1365":"1365","1265":"1265","1320":"1320","about 1343":"um 1343","about 1320":"um 1320","1407":"1407","1318":"1318","1306":"1306","1328":"1328","Altyre, Morayshire, Scotland":"Moray, Schottland, United Kingdom","Dumfries, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Dumfries, Dumfriesshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Morayshire, Scotland":"Elginshire, Scotland","Argyle, Scotland":"Argyll, Schottland, United Kingdom","Altyre House, Morayshire, Scotland":"Altyre House, Elginshire, Scotland","lifeSummary":"Als Sir Thomas Comyn 1292 in Altyre House, Elginshire, Scotland geboren wurde, war sein Vater Sir Robert Comyn 31 und seine Mutter Margaret Comyn 28. Er hat um 1343 in Scotland Helen Arbuthnot geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 3 Söhne. Er starb 1365 im Alter von 73 Jahren in Scotland."},"ht":{"1292–1365":"1292–1365","1280–Male":"1280–Desede","1296–Female":"1296–Desede","1328–Female":"1328–Desede","1365–Male":"1365–Desede","1318–1407":"1318–1407","1320–Male":"1320–Desede","–Male":"Desede","1261–1306":"1261–1306","1265–Female":"1265–Desede","about 1291":"about 1291","1296":"1296","1261":"1261","1292":"1292","abt 1365":"about 1365","1280":"1280","about 1318":"about 1318","1365":"1365","1265":"1265","1320":"1320","about 1343":"about 1343","about 1320":"about 1320","1407":"1407","1318":"1318","1306":"1306","1328":"1328","Altyre, Morayshire, Scotland":"Moray, Ecosse, United Kingdom","Dumfries, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Dumfries, Dumfrie